   Congressman David E. Bonior
     [DEB_and_Safe_Schools.jpg] [Clean_Water_Photo.jpg]
   [DEB_with_Seniors_and_Affordable_Prescriptions.jpg]
     Congressman Bonior is working hard to ensure that our children are
   safe in school and get the quality education they deserve. More

   One of Congressman Bonior's top priorities is ensuring that our water,
   particularly that of the Great Lakes, is abundant, clean, and safe for
   our families to enjoy. More



   Affordable prescriptions are a necessity for our seniors. As the cost
   of prescription medicine continues to rise, our seniors need the option
   of getting prescription medicine coverage through Medicare. More


